longBusinessSummary: Wihlborgs Fastigheter AB (publ), a property company, owns, develops, rents, and manages commercial properties in the Öresund region, Sweden. Wihlborgs Fastigheter AB (publ) was founded in 1924 and is headquartered in Malmö, Sweden.
